* .NET Core Version: `6`
* Windows version: `Win10 21H2
* Does the bug reproduce also in WPF for .NET Framework 4.8?: `Never test.`
* Is this bug related specifically to tooling in Visual Studio (e.g. XAML Designer, Code editing, etc...)?: `NO`
